edu.brown.cs.wh7.Trie

Class Trie

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.wh7.Trie.Trie

  • public class Trie
extends Object
    Class to represent a Prefix Trie for storing words in a corpus. The trie has 3 lookup algorithms to find words in a tree: prefix matching, whitespace matching, and maximum levenshtein edit distance.
    Author:
    wh7
